  "body": "_this should be a UI/UX improvement_\r\n\r\n# Feature Issue\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a user, I want to be informed that I need to transfer tokens only to the predefined main wallet to buy a username with it.\r\n\r\nBack story: I played around with the app and created a second wallet. Then I transferred SNT to it to buy a username, just to realize you can pay for it only from the main wallet at the moment. With fees close to $30 and a username cost of about $1 it's annoying to run into this.\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n\r\nI think this can be easily achieved even with a simple alert or note where you copy the address or similar.\r\n\r\n",
